# agents.mmd — {{AGENT_NAME}} context file
# Loaded into the agent's working memory at boot.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this template per agent:
#        cp agents.mmd.template ../../customers/<slug>/<agent-name>.mmd
#   2. Replace all {{PLACEHOLDERS}} with real values.
#   3. Reference this file from the customer YAML:
#        second_brain:
#          enabled: true
#          seed_path: "config/customers/<slug>/<agent-name>.mmd"
#   4. The HermesInstaller uploads this file to the cloud computer
#      during step 5 (load_second_brain), where the runtime reads it
#      into the agent's working context on every boot.
#
# VERTICAL-SPECIFIC TEMPLATES:
#   See config/context-templates/ for ready-made templates by vertical:
#     marketing.mmd.template  — outbound, content, lead-gen agents
#     law.mmd.template        — legal research, contract review agents
#     insurance.mmd.template  — claims processing, underwriting agents
#   Copy the closest one and customize.

