## Second Brain

Your Obsidian vault is at `/data/obsidian/`.

### Read from (knowledge sources):
- `company/` — customer company profile, org chart, brand guidelines
- `personas/` — ideal customer profiles, buyer personas
- `templates/` — approved message templates, proposal structures
- `meetings/` — meeting notes synced from Granola
- `playbooks/` — standard operating procedures for your role
- `history/` — past interactions, decisions, outcomes

### Write to (discovery outputs):
- `discoveries/` — new insights, patterns, learnings from your work
- `drafts/` — work-in-progress content awaiting human review
- `logs/` — daily activity summaries (auto-generated)

### Update rules:
- Always append, never overwrite existing notes
- Use ISO-8601 timestamps in filenames: `2026-05-12-topic.md`
- Tag discoveries with `#{{AGENT_NAME}}` so the operator can filter
- If you learn something about the customer that isn't in `company/`, write it to `discoveries/` and flag for review


